reviewText: I put the DVD in two diferent players and it did not play at all. The screen on the player and tv. Showed the error message: "No play. No playback feature."

This DVD is not in the widescreen format. The sound and video are bad. You can buy the same video collection from the Warners Bros DVD ZZ Top Collection. If you want this collection, buy the WB DVD collection because it has good video and sound.
